<bibRefCitation author="Hartert, E." box="[351,605,272,294]" pageId="85" pageNumber="85" pagination="123 - 178" refId="ref119004" refString="Hartert, E. 1919 a. Types of birds in the Tring Museum. B. Types in the general collection. Novitates Zoologicae 26: 123 - 178." type="journal article" year="1919">Hartert (1919a: 144)</bibRefCitation>
